Git

git --version
git config --global user.name "w3schools-test"        --Now let Git know who you are
git config --global user.email "test@w3schools.com"

Creating Git Folder
mkdir myproject
cd myproject

Initialize Git
git init


git status

Files in your Git repository
	Tracked - files that Git knows about and are added to the repository
	Untracked - files that are in your working directory, but not added to the repository


adding files to staging
git add index.html
git add --all


commit
git commit -m "First release of Hello World!"

Git Commit Log
git log

Git Help
git commit -help

create branch			-- git branch hello-world-images
switching of branch		--git checkout hello-world-images

